Fun not perfect movie. Pleased with how the Skywalker series wrapped up. Knew no matter what it was gonna be better than TLJ

To be honest: only the last Jedi has been more boring than this episode. The story was kind of confusing to me and had to many turning points in my opinion.
The good: awesome CG, Kylo Ren, Han Solo,  Lando Calrissian, the emperor
The bad: bad character development for Rey, plot/story gaps or mistakes which makes you wonder (why shoot the troopers in the hangar when you use mind control a moment later?), recycled battles

Overall a movie that was ok but could have been so much more. One could argue that they butchered the saga with this conclusion.
